{"id": "ChIJfbqeegDDwoARyB32pm8erL0", "rating": 4.6, "userRatingCount": 41, "displayName": {"text": "Tosakko Ramen & Yakitori", "languageCode": "zh"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJfbqeegDDwoARyB32pm8erL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OM1MwSlNVa2hGTjJSRlRYWkpObXRQWHpZeVRGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "“I love Torigoya in downtown Little Tokyo for their yakitori, but I recently found this spot much closer to home—and in my opinion, it’s even better than average (though some people might not agree). The yakitori is fresh, perfectly grilled, and you can tell the Japanese chef really knows his stuff over the charcoal. The ramen was solid and flavorful too. Servers were super nice and attentive—we enjoyed everything a lot. I’m so glad a legit, high-quality yakitori place opened in the neighborhood. Only wish: they’d offer ginger and wasabi on the side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "“I love Torigoya in downtown Little Tokyo for their yakitori, but I recently found this spot much closer to home—and in my opinion, it’s even better than average (though some people might not agree). The yakitori is fresh, perfectly grilled, and you can tell the Japanese chef really knows his stuff over the charcoal. The ramen was solid and flavorful too. Servers were super nice and attentive—we enjoyed everything a lot. I’m so glad a legit, high-quality yakitori place opened in the neighborhood. Only wish: they’d offer ginger and wasabi on the side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bruce jk Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117820444488965871044/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxSSidTkelOShU-oZQYKTGNxpqlOAODAyLj471z_XGWakOMJU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-16T02:44:22.937600993Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OM1MwSlNVa2hGTjJSRlRYWkpObXRQWHpZeVRGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OM1MwSlNVa2hGTjJSRlRYWkpObXRQWHpZeVRGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3007a9eba7d:0xbdac1e6fa6f61dc8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfbqeegDDwoARyB32pm8erL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sWmEzTk9ZVEJSVWxsQ1dFZFJSVmxTTURKTVkzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great place to eat! Everything was absolutely delicious. Service was outstanding! Will definitely go back soon", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great place to eat! Everything was absolutely delicious. Service was outstanding! Will definitely go back soon", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Victoria Sandoval", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115664019414744332956/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgiSNtm_DQh559tpGTudlCSnTwBA7zwgaz5Vqpt2aXG34wT6U=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-10T02:43:39.136280380Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sWmEzTk9ZVEJSVWxsQ1dFZFJSVmxTTURKTVkzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sWmEzTk9ZVEJSVWxsQ1dFZFJSVmxTTURKTVkzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3007a9eba7d:0xbdac1e6fa6f61dc8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfbqeegDDwoARyB32pm8erL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkeWRESjJNR3RSYVRCdFpFNHhWRzlxWkdwVVZrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great atmosphere with good food. It was nice and quiet, unlike typical ramen restaurants. The servers were friendly and attentive. Would come again for the yakitori.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great atmosphere with good food. It was nice and quiet, unlike typical ramen restaurants. The servers were friendly and attentive. Would come again for the yakitori.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nana Horii", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116921067146436887503/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdpktaHqbLIT7iG33puuYepB6Y23SgP9aA4AHqs_pPGPIi_gQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-25T23:36:31.471089958Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkeWRESjJNR3RSYVRCdFpFNHhWRzlxWkdwVVZrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkeWRESjJNR3RSYVRCdFpFNHhWRzlxWkdwVVZrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3007a9eba7d:0xbdac1e6fa6f61dc8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfbqeegDDwoARyB32pm8erL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sSmNXbFNVRmRZU2xwUGNYTm5VV2RRYkdaZk5tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My fiancé and I were needing a place to eat before a movie and came across this lovely place. We had no clue it was their first day and we were so blown away by the food! I had the rich mazesoba and my fiancé had the signature ramen and my goodness, they were both phenomenal. The service was very kind, the owner and his wife were there asking for feedback, and they gave us additional food as well. Please go give this place some love, it's showing a ton of promise and my fiancé and I will be back for more!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My fiancé and I were needing a place to eat before a movie and came across this lovely place. We had no clue it was their first day and we were so blown away by the food! I had the rich mazesoba and my fiancé had the signature ramen and my goodness, they were both phenomenal. The service was very kind, the owner and his wife were there asking for feedback, and they gave us additional food as well. Please go give this place some love, it's showing a ton of promise and my fiancé and I will be back for more!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Delaney Heil (NotQuiteChrome)", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106823469415011980445/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3i5kJSXVUEbA-9__pdSk80vpQb4TYJ0FNNW1G552oMlQXaJmD=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-20T23:32:23.661133102Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sSmNXbFNVRmRZU2xwUGNYTm5VV2RRYkdaZk5tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25sSmNXbFNVRmRZU2xwUGNYTm5VV2RRYkdaZk5tYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3007a9eba7d:0xbdac1e6fa6f61dc8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfbqeegDDwoARyB32pm8erL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWNE0xQlRjMVV0TkdaSmIwTnJjRUp1VTBGVVRVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We were fortunate enough to wander into this beautiful restaurant on their soft opening day! It was a lovely experience and we loved our food and drink. The Yakitori was delicious and fresh while the service was impeccable. Looking forward to our next visit!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We were fortunate enough to wander into this beautiful restaurant on their soft opening day! It was a lovely experience and we loved our food and drink. The Yakitori was delicious and fresh while the service was impeccable. Looking forward to our next visit!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Brittany Walloch-Key", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101123525594470775822/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRX4E44y93_v0REvYc07313RBr0BLW7jMhYohGozrNTgWFYoA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-19T00:39:49.074844786Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xWNE0xQlRjMVV0TkdaSmIwTnJjRUp1VTBGVVRVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/